Usage: copyOaRestoreFiles [-help] <fromLib> <fromCell> <fromView> <toLib>
                          <toCell> <toView>

-help         # Prints out the command usage
<fromLib>     # Specifies source library name (string, required)
<fromCell>    # Specifies source cell name (string, required)
<fromView>    # Specifies source view name (string, required)
<toLib>       # Specifies destination library name (string, required)
<toCell>      # Specifies destination cell name (string, required)
<toView>      # Specifies destination view name (string, required)